  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK622">
<l>veḷḷat taṉaiya viṭumpai yaṟivuṭaiyā</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷatti ṉuḷḷak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A flood of troubles will be overcome by the (courageous) thought which the minds of the wise will entertain, even in sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
